<del rend="erased">des <expan>v<ex>er</ex>greiffens</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></del></ab></add> etc <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſteet</expan> Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l6">ſelbs wol . daʒ niht notdurft ıſt daʒ wır eẅch <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> eıns <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_13_r1l8">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſull<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del> ſeın 
